name: 90s Keanu Reeves「LoRa」
description:
main trigger word : Kreeves

additional words : beard , man, long hair.

  • 2 in 1 LoRa with young beardless Keanu Reeves which can be triggered with just Kreeves, with a slightly older (but still 2000s era) Keanu being triggered by adding a beard prompt

  • Since young keanu with long hair had such a feminine feel, the AI may confuse and produce females who look like Keanu, which is why I added man as well, not needed everywhere; but it's a failsafe.

  • recommended LoRa strength : 0.8

this model was used for generating previews.

if you like my stuff pls consider supporting me on Kofi

<3

modelVersions.name: v1.0
modelVersions.description: may produce some face artifacts at lora strength 1 occasionally, I personally recommend 0.8
